	\arrow["\rs"', dotted, two heads, from=2-1, to=2-2]
	\arrow[draw=none, from=1, to=0]
\end{tikzcd}\]

\noindent    Because $\gos{\rs} \subset \inccon{\preceq}{\rr\cup\rs}$, the second diagram follows.

(3) The following diagram clearly holds if the sequence of reduction steps from |b| to |d| is the same as the sequence of reduction steps from |b| to |a| to |d|:

% https://q.uiver.app/?
\[\begin{tikzcd}
